ore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T05:11:59.000Z","msg":"手勢慣左4線<br />\n到轉5線係果時係要d時間適應"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T05:18:11.000Z","msg":"咁5線轉4線呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見啲人話4線已經夠彈曬啲pop歌<br />\nChing係因為咩原因彈5線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T08:16:49.000Z","msg":"彈開五線冇理由會轉"},{"pid":"9d810f1740043a35aff00337c3db41eb312eeb71","tid":2139084,"uid":10267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:02:56.000Z","msg":"小弟教開一般男學生都用到5線<br />\n當然一開始pick up黎講4線會再易啲上手<br />\n如果想一枝走天涯，想玩&amp;學多啲唔同style先，就5線較著數<br />\n<br />\n大部分學生想玩canton pop, j rock, classic 歐美rock/heavy嘢都係有條low B 會著數d"},{"pid":"53a1802fb474dc484af186cbd5138d55e6d7f910","tid":2139084,"uid":109090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:08:41.000Z","msg":"其實無咩分別<br />\n要轉既話係要熟習，但唔爭得多"},{"pid":"19d2bd7c14be0d7ebff439cf89f3bfbee64d3b8b","tid":2139084,"uid":260946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:33:16.000Z","msg":"如果你肯等shipping嘅話，Harley Benton無得輸；$2000 6/5線包shipping都仲有找<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thomann.de/gb/harley_benton_b_550_white_progressive_series.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thomann.de%2Fgb%2Fharley_benton_b_550_white_progressive_series.htm&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd9B4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=cfef6571\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thomann.de/gb/harley_benton_b_550_white_progressive_series.htm</a><br />\n仲要其實好好聲，識人有部sandberg同strandberg headless，然候佢都要keep住部harley<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e767c4f7403fc974e279ae94eebb3c02fad702","tid":2139084,"uid":260946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b89620b534dde486ff0eccbd148f3526d76609b","tid":2139084,"uid":83531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c25823edcf0729d35cdb0bede3987aa4ee251496","tid":